def dropduplicates(df):
    for index in df.index:
        if df.loc[index,"Tm"]=='TOT':
            count=index
            count+=1
            df.loc[index,"Tm"]= df.loc[count,"Tm"]
            if df.loc[count,"G"]<df.loc[count+1,"G"]:
                count=index
                count+=2
                df.loc[index,"Tm"]= df.loc[count,"Tm"]

def newyeardf(df, allstars,rtg,adv,stand):
    df['Player'] = df['Player'].str.replace('*', '')
    rtg['Player'] = rtg['Player'].str.replace('*', '')
    rtg = rtg[['Player','G','ORtg','DRtg']].reset_index()
    adv = adv[['Player', 'G','PER', 'TS%', '3PAr',
       'FTr', 'ORB%', 'DRB%', 'TRB%', 'AST%', 'STL%', 'BLK%', 'TOV%', 'USG%',
       'OWS', 'DWS', 'WS', 'WS/48', 'OBPM', 'DBPM', 'BPM', 'VORP']]
    x = []
    y = []
    for i in df['Player']:
        x.append(i)
    for i in x:
        y.append(i.split("\\", 1)[0])
    df['Player'] = y    
    df.assign(Group='A')
    a = []
    def makeitalist(file,col):
        l1st = []
        for i in file[col]:
            l1st.append(i)
        return l1st
    allstars2021 = makeitalist(allstars, 'Players')
    for i in df['Player']:
        for j in allstars2021:
            if i == j:
                a.append(1)
                break
            else:
                continue
        condition = i in allstars2021
        if condition != True:
            a.append(0)
    df['Allstar'] = a
    c = []
    d = []
    r = []
    s = []
    #df = dropduplicates(df)
    for i in rtg['Player']:
        c.append(i)
    for i in c:
        d.append(i.split("\\", 1)[0])
    for i in adv['Player']:
        r.append(i)
    for i in c:
        s.append(i.split("\\", 1)[0])
    rtg['Player'] = d  
    adv['Player'] = s
    rtg.assign(Group='A')
    #rtg = dropduplicates(rtg)
    #adv = dropduplicates(adv)
    df = pd.merge(df,rtg)
    df = pd.merge(df,adv)
    #df = pd.merge(df, adv)
    #adv = adv.drop('G', 1)
    #adv2 = adv.drop('Player', 1)
    #df.reset_index()
    #hi = adv2.reset_index()
    #df = df.join(hi, lsuffix='_left')
    #df = df.drop('index_left', 1)
    #df = df.drop('index', 1)
    df['3P%'] = df['3P%'].fillna(0)
    df['FT%'] = df['FT%'].fillna(0)
    df = df.loc[df["G"] > 23]
    df['NRtg'] = df['ORtg'] - df['DRtg']
    listats = makeitalist(df, 'Tm')
    o = []
    for i in listats:
        if i == 'NOH':
            o.append('NOP')
        elif i == 'CHA':
            o.append('CHO')
        else:
            o.append(i)
    df['Tm'] = o
    stand = stand[['Unnamed: 1', 'All-Star']]
    stand = stand.iloc[1: , :]
    stand.columns = ['Team', 'Record']
    stand[['Wins', 'Losses']] = stand['Record'].str.split("-", expand=True)
    stand["Wins"] = pd.to_numeric(stand["Wins"])
    stand["Losses"] = pd.to_numeric(stand["Losses"])
    stand['WinPct'] = (stand['Wins'])/(stand['Wins'] + stand['Losses'])
    for index in stand.index:
        if stand.loc[index,"Team"] == 'New Orleans Pelicans':
            stand.loc[index,"Team"] = 'NOP'
        if stand.loc[index,"Team"] == 'Los Angeles Lakers':
            stand.loc[index,"Team"] = 'LAL'
        stand.loc[index,"Team"]= stand.loc[index,"Team"][0:3].upper()
        if stand.loc[index,"Team"] == 'BRO':
            stand.loc[index,"Team"] = 'BRK'
        if stand.loc[index,"Team"] == 'LOS':
            stand.loc[index,"Team"] = 'LAC'
        if stand.loc[index,"Team"] == 'NEW':
            stand.loc[index,"Team"] = 'NYK'
        if stand.loc[index,"Team"] == 'GOL':
            stand.loc[index,"Team"] = 'GSW'
        if stand.loc[index,"Team"] == 'CHA':
            stand.loc[index,"Team"] = 'CHO'
        if stand.loc[index,"Team"] == 'SAN':
            stand.loc[index,"Team"] = 'SAS'
        if stand.loc[index,"Team"] == 'OKL':
            stand.loc[index,"Team"] = 'OKC'
    df['WinPct'] = 0
    for index in df.index:
        for jindex in stand.index:
            if df.loc[index,"Tm"] == stand.loc[jindex,"Team"]:
                df.loc[index,"WinPct"] = stand.loc[jindex,"WinPct"]
    return df

def accuracy(x):
    i = 1
    trainlist = []
    testlist = []
    y= stats['Allstar']
    while i < 50:
        xtrain, xtest, ytrain, ytest = train_test_split(x, y, test_size=0.25, random_state = i)
        train=sm.Logit(ytrain, sm.add_constant(xtrain), method = 'kwargs').fit()
        xpredtest= train.predict(sm.add_constant(xtest))
        xpredtrain= train.predict(sm.add_constant(xtrain))
        trainlist.append(metrics.accuracy_score(ytrain,(xpredtrain).round()))
        testlist.append(metrics.accuracy_score(ytest,(xpredtest).round()))
        i += 1
    print("Train Accuracy",  mean(trainlist), "\nTest Accuracy", mean(testlist) )

import itertools
def combo(features):
    all_combinations = []
    for r in range(len(features) + 1):

        combinations_object = itertools.combinations(features, r)
        combinations_list = list(combinations_object)
        all_combinations += combinations_list

    return all_combinations
